{
  "stem": "14387.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband's family-- women, children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two of his brothers, after they returned to Trondheim, were sitting in their home and listening to the radio, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I don't know if they were reported, or how the soldiers came to break into their homes and found them listening to the radio.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took them out, took them-- arrested them, put them in Kristiansten, which is a fortress in Trondheim, and shot them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother-in-law was in Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The reason she didn't go back-- she would have gone back, too, but her daughter became sick, and was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she didn't go back to Trondheim, because she was staying with her-- she stayed with her daughter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was sitting, listening to-- to the radio in Stockholm, and heard the announcement that her two sons had been shot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "See they were-- because they had monopolized the business in Trondheim, of gentlemen's wear, they were a fairly well-known family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they announced over the radio that her two sons had been shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother-in-law heard that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, nothing more to be said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, some of them were sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three, four little children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Four small children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two brothers and their wives went to Auschwitz, and some of them escaped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can say that they escaped with a little help of the Norwegian, non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They hid them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One sister-in-law-- the sister-in-law whose husband was shot, she took the two children, one child on her back, on skis, crossed the-- crossed across-- you know that's-- I'm talking about crossing a whole country.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you know the-- if you've ever looked at a map of Norway, Norway's a very narrow country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Trondheim is on the coast.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
